{"tid":1647923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日下晝我要見到美國旗海喺九龍出現","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T06:18:10.000Z","uid":124636,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c60c9286393079118941f51c4609e5a109193715","tid":1647923,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"侵侵唔理香港？我屌你老母啦，你地第一日識侵仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有侵侵話香港嘅抗議會自己搞掂，冇話抗爭者暴力，冇話希望香港快D回復和平。自己搞掂即係暗示支共你唔好插手呀，你地喊驚咁做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵侵話香港示威者人數已經減少好多，咁即係如果人數多嘅話佢個attention又會去番香港到啦，所以陣間3點一定要多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BBOhaOSAgSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBBOhaOSAgSU&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=bcd9655e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BBOhaOSAgSU</a><br />\n侵侵前幾日特別提到見到香港手足拎美國旗同佢個樣去遊行，嗌make hong kong great again，如果陣間個個都拎美國旗，唔知會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撇除侵侵唔講，美國民間因為nba事件搞到反支情緒高漲，stand with hong kong得到更廣泛關注，如果今晚成個twitter都係香港九龍出現美國旗海，點都對國際戰線有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ccddb2c9f8d482a20fec8b0e5d552e462f4005","tid":1647923,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfbc538c218d2556df182797f86a1fd5dce8866","tid":1647923,"uid":124636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">O say can you see, by the dawn's early light</span>"},{"pid":"bddadb6ecbe35e96207d7c39571686cf621a49a8","tid":1647923,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84bc599c5a4e71b38c01772a47ff7f5cd9222a2d","tid":1647923,"uid":124636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"What so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming"},{"pid":"f24f6403fd87eb9879597c620f8531874154ec59","tid":1647923,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"USA！USA！USA！美國國旗！"},{"pid":"d1a70b60e5c61720f9cc532566ceaef31b27d555","tid":1647923,"uid":150083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"10.12 反緊急法遊行<br />\n時間：3:00pm<br />\n地點：尖沙咀鐘樓至深水埗運動場"},{"pid":"a3bb1992d3d98ea14a0ace6f84abf55f49c957b9","tid":1647923,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d978fd71db26916dec326fc24df6a81168fc874","tid":1647923,"uid":124636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight,"},{"pid":"6c3886d6d5309ed1c00c699b439d37e48aef850a","tid":1647923,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1d951fda85f7c3c54c5f3b9a3c9b53fd5e85f5","tid":1647923,"uid":124636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"O'er the ramparts we watched, were so gallantly streaming?"},{"pid":"23942ce794351d319afcc1cf804c6ab74b04c90b","tid":1647923,"uid":6964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"And the rockets red glare, the bomb bursting in air"},{"pid":"07d99c8db2154c869a2a74ce4d209ee96a8acea5","tid":1647923,"uid":93000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h